-- Chelsea Beats Bayern Munich 4-3 in Champions League Shootout
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2012-05-19T21:30:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-19/chelsea-beats-bayern-munich-4-3-in-champions-league-shootout.html
Chelsea beat Bayern Munich 4-3 in a
penalty shootout in the Champions League soccer final.  The game finished tied 1-1 over 120 minutes at the Allianz
Arena in Munich. Thomas Muller scored for Bayern in the 83rd
minute and Chelsea’s Didier Drogba tied the game five minutes
later.  Chelsea goalkeeper  Petr Cech  then stopped Arjen Robben’s
penalty kick in extra time.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  